# Human approval is required for changes to security-sensitive infrastructure,
# regardless of what any autonomous agent proposes. Enable branch protection on
# `main` with "Require review from Code Owners" for this to be enforced.
#
# These are the paths a prompt-injected loop could try to weaken:
#   - the public composite-action API (consumed by other repos)
#   - the workflows (privilege/secret scope, egress policy)
#   - the guard hooks and loop settings (the deterministic guardrails themselves)

/.github/actions/**       @eliihen
/.github/workflows/**     @eliihen
/.github/CODEOWNERS       @eliihen
/.claude/settings.json    @eliihen
/scripts/hooks/**         @eliihen
